summary: Professional Samsung Galaxy Note 3 Smartphone BLUE LED Car Charger

reviewText: I mainly purchased this charger because my wife did not have any other means of recharging her phone other than a wall outlet.  Since she spends a reasonable amount of time driving around town it was necessary to provide her with an alternative means of charging her phone.  Plus we discovered her battery can run down pretty quickly sometimes so I wanted to make sure she had a means of charging her phone in case of emergency.  We are pleased with the performance of this charger.  It is easy to use and easy to store in a console as well.
summary: Very effective for charging phone in car

reviewText: It charges my Rugby fast while the car is on.  My previous phone & car charger charged while the car was running or not.
Very pleased with the charger. Works good and charges my phone. In the past I had purchased ones that did not work well and this one is top notch.
This case is amazing! Its easy to put together and it really protects your phone. If your a clutz like me this is a great case to have.

This case is pretty shock proof, but not very good at keeping water out.  The fatal flaw is where the glass meets the frame. I can see right into the case.Also, use lock tite for the screws, they loosen all the time.

The case cracked & cracked my phone with it. I sent pictures to the seller & have not heard back from them. It was only a week after i got the case & the phone was in my pocketbook it should not have cracked at all. I'm still waiting to see what they are going to do about it. Very disappointed in the case.
the retracability is so fast! easy to control. quality of the plastic is okay. you get what you pay for!

Nicely made and very convenient.  Charger cords are forever getting tangled so the retractable feature of this one is quite nice.  Powerful, too - it snaps that cord back into the casing in a jiffy.  Both ends (12V and phone) fit snugly.  Very pleased with this item.
There were cheaper ones at Amazon but I chose this because of the blue light. I know it's crazy but my wife can use it on her tablet while we're in the car. It's a good product.
Great to have and you can charge your phone on those long drives home. Been using it daily. Great product

I ordered this to fit my new phone i purchased. I liked the fact they were easy to put on but i did not like the fact i had to cut them but seller was great and gave me a discount for customer satisfaction . I would probably recommend these to a friend
The Nokia N95 8gh phone crystal case is a very handy and easy to carry case. it is so close fitting to the phone that you would hardly know it on when moving aroud with the phone in my pocket.
it just lasted 24 hours. Then my honest opinion it's that no body should buy it.

I don't normally review but we are a business, we have about 50 of these Note 10.1, 2014 and it's just easier to use this with a usb device like a flash drive for files and transfer versus internet, and we have pretty big files.  Sure we use dropbox, but you don't always have wifi and in a business, you need reliability and something that works.We've purchased the white and black versions, both work great.  Tip, verify your format on your drive, this will not see it unless it's FAT32 I believe.I left the same review for the white one, but it appears the same item, different color so sorry if there are duplicate reviews =).
summary: We use the white and black versions, both work great.

reviewText: The flower detail on this snap on case is really subtle. The only complaint would be that the edges of the case are not completely painted with the design. The case stays on; it has only come off once when I dropped the phone.

When i first received this case, I thought it was great. It looked good and it fit perfectly. After about a week of normal use, the design started to come off around the edges to reveal a silver coating underneath. Within a month it just didn't look good anymore and i took it off.

I loved this case which is why I bought it. The two pieces snap together, which I thought would be ok, however, the top piece does not stay snapped together with the bottom. If it would stay together, the case would be great.
This case didn't fit right! It felt like the front and back were from 2 different cases! Very unhappy with it!

I believe life should be fun so when I can find little things to make ordinary things fun why not!!I have these on all my apple devices. My favorite it the red with the white mickey heads because I love red and white Polka dots. I  just bought a polka dot skin for the iphone and this button works perfect with it.As a disney fan it is fun to have these little things that say hey I am a fan but with out it being in your face.I have had mine for quite a while now and they have stayed on through some tuff loving. My daughter has a few on her devices as well and they stick on great. I have not tried to take them off because I love them But I am sure if you wanted to switch out you could.  I like that it came in a 6 pack as I have many I-items. So between my daughter and i we used the whole package.
summary: To fun Must have for Disney fans and apple prodcuts

reviewText: A fun and whimsical way to protect your phone, easy to put on! Owl lovers will adore this case :)
The paint scratches off and it feels pretty cheap.  But hey if you like the graphics get it.  offers light protection
Fast shipping and good sturdy product. Fits the Samsung Galaxy proclaim perfectly. Will definitely buy from again. Hoping to see more owl designs
summary: love it. even more colorful than photo

reviewText: This case was exactly what my wife was looking for. It's a perfect fit and is very stylish. The item was shipped super fast and the seller was very friendly.

I was supposed to recieve this on the 24th, however I recieved it today, so it was great shipping :)It doesn't come with a tracking code for you to check constantly, however. But it's fine for me because it's something small and to forget about within a couple days.I recieved it as pictured and have one on right now. It's a hard plastic, rounded feeling that's smooth but hard to get used to. I have a white iPhone 5 and it's working perfectly. It looks great and I've already been getting compliments from my friends. It sticks on well, too.Because this was sort of an off-market kind of thing, it looks like it's shady to buy however yoj weren't at risk that much(Costed around 5 bucks at the time). I ordered it anyways and it turned out great.

The type of case and overall design is just as expected. However I noticed a few very small chips of paint/colored foil missing right above the Owl's nose,eyes and around the camera hole. I realize that over time these chips cannot be helped but I hadn't expected it on a product straight out of packaging. The manufacturer should put an extra protective layer over the design to increase it's resilience.
summary: Cute but with a few very small chips in coloring

reviewText: Haven't used it yet, but I did check to see if it fit my phone after reading other reviews that said it didn't fit to good. It fits my phone perfectly. Even though it is a backup case, I'm pretty sure it will meet my expectations.
Looks just like the picture. Goes on easily, holes line up. Makes the phone look great. Does just what it is supposed to do, for the price it is excellent!  Thanks

I just received my case in the mail today and it love it! It seems to be durable so far (which is a plus because the kids like to steal my phone). It looks exactly like it does in the picture when it is on the phone, off the phone it is bright pink THE CASE IS SEE THROUGH =)! It got here quick too, ALSO i do NOT have the i9100 model i have the i777 version and it fits just like it is supposed to, Wonderful product and for the price i will be ordering the different colors
Great material for protecting your phone. I love it and the color and I'm sure you will enjoy it too!

This cover has been the best cover I have ever had. I am not someone who let's her phone drop, yet with this one it dropped alot and this case truly has been a life-saver. Not a scratch on the phone or the screen and the phone has fallen face down and nothing. I wish they made one for the GS3 and I would gladly buy it again.
fits perfectly on the S2 i9100 ! great grip on the phone and purple is very pretty! recommend this product 100%
It fits perfectly my Samsung SII i9100 (international version, BE CAREFUL). The material feels really good and I love it.
For the price, it looks good.  The only downturn is it offers no protection for the front but I haven't use it yet.

The cover is alright.  It's great to keep the phone protected.  Design starts wearing off right away.  Worth the price of the cover itself, but not worth what is being charged for shipping.  I ordered 3 of these for $3 each and paid $18 shipping.  They were all shipped together in a recycled priority mail package.  While I appreciate the environmentally conscious packaging, it certainly was not worth $18!
summary: OK Cover, Too much for shipping...

reviewText: This cover is excellent.  I love the colors and it does a great job of protecting my phone.  I dropped the phone (twice!) on the street.  The cover got cracked and no doubt saved the phone from cracking.  I ordered two more covers.  I'll order them again if I need them.
summary: rubberized plastic zebra pattern phone cover

reviewText: I really like this cover. The buttons on the sides of the phone are covered by this case.  I like that, not the "holes" that you'd find with a hard cover.  When I got it in the mail, I was taken aback because it wasn't as dark as I had expected, but once I put it on my phone, I realized the case is a "see-through" that looks darker with the black phone.
More than worth the money.  My daughterloves it and so does her friends.
look better in pic its not white in between it silver in the picture it look like it had white in it other wise it ok

loved the colors and pattern on this and couldn't wait to get it.  Seemed to fit decent, but not great.  After about 3 weeks, it cracked on the side and then just broke off altogether.  Horrible deal!!!!!!!!!  I am VERY disappointed

I was soooo excited about this case!  It looked so cute!  But it lasted a whopping 1 week before it practically disintegrated around my phone and just fell off.  The plastic is not very sturdy at all. For the 1 week that it "functioned", I could feel my phone moving around inside it. Don't be fooled by the fun, bright colors!!

This case is pretty and feels really cool. But it snapped really easily and is not easy to get on and off! After about a week the front snapped in half and chipped and faded. I was very disappointed, i never drop it. Then like a week later the back cracked off and was badly chipped. It also took a while to send to my house. I even tried to glue it back together! I am disappointed with this case, it is not recommended for quality!
I would not recommend this cover to anyone.  I purchased this for my daughters cell phone and it broke within two weeks.  Planning to replace it with a silicone cover to ensure it will hold up.

When I located this Iphone case/cover I thought it was very nice looking!As I am into Butterfly any & everything.  Although, don't want to sacrifice quality either with no matter what product it is that I am purchasing!With this product, when I received it...it has a part at the bottom corner where is it what I would call "chipped/broken" out of it!I must admit that through my frustration and disappointment I didn't want to be inconvenienced with having to go through any additional costs or time consuming issues in order to get it returned and replaced!I have just kept in mind where I purchased it from and the condition so that I don't make that mistake again!So, if there is a way that this without a whole lot of hassle can be replaced I would appreciate it!Thank You,May Hughart[...]

Amazon carries old style phone covers when retail stores don't.  My granddaughter picked through several items that were available for her phone and is very happy.  We've bought several covers for Ipods and phones through Amazon and always get quick delivery.
I purchased this case for my daughters phone and the piece of crap broke in a short time. Don't waste your money!

This is a great case/protector! Very good quality! I drop my phone ALOT, and all the other cases I have had always fell off, I have had not had that issue at all w/ this one. Also, the artwork on this one is very detailed and looks awsome! You will not be disappointed w/ this case at all!!
I've only had it a couple months, and it has never been dropped or abused and it falls off my phone every time I pick my phone up. It does not fit like it should, and never did.

This cover doesn't cover the light sensor like the other cover I bought. It fit perfectly; wasn't too loose and never fell off. It wasn't cheap, flimsy plastic. I loved it and received so many compliments.

Got it...like it..it is pretty but it is not easy to get off.  I need the clip part so I keep a tiny screw driver in my purse so when my phone freeze & need to pop out battery I can get case off.  It is durable...I have dropped it many times and still looks the same...no crack & not faded.
Loved the product. It works perfect for my voyager. It is very cute and I've gotten a lot of compliments. Very durable. dropped it one too many times and the cover alwas saves it.
Item was received and did not snap onto the phone it was designed for. It was chipped and looked used/broken. I could not use it and No refund was issued.
I ordered this for my daughter.  She loved the colors and it fit the phone very nicely. She wants another one.

Ordered this case, it looked great, fit well, and had the belt clip with it. Except that the color started chipping off within a week or so. But you get what you pay for. Still looked very good for the few bucks I paid, just don't expect it to last that long.

Fits the phone great. Also, it makes turning on the display a little bit harder. As I carry my phone in my pocket, that's just fine by me; it helps the battery last that much longer. No changes to sound or display; case makes the phone easier to grip.

Received promptly. Stickers are not too thin. Won't tear easily. Love the colors. Stickers are shiny and bright. Decorates my phone button, makes it look new. sleek design. Will make any phone look up to date.
My wife really loved this phone case.  It came right on time and was put to use immediately.  Very pleased.

I drop my phone- alot. So i got this case.  When i first opened it the case looked a little faded, like it had already been used. but it just looks like that normally.  after using if for a couple months the design is still absolutely fine with a couple chips around the edge from dropping it.  the only downside to this is the front part can not snap on completely on the right side or the touch screen won't work any more.  it still stays on fine and does not affect the phone at all. just snap it on all the way and then edge it off a little and you're good to go. if you drop your phone alot and it causes it to flip open, the clips onthe back piece of the case at the top of the keyboard on either side may break off. this happened to me and the case is just a little loose then. if it bothers you, just take 2 little rolls of tape and stick on the inside of the case in the corners and it stays on just fine and you won't notice any difference. i was really glad i bought this case and all of my friends tell me how cute/ cool it is.
Very cute and fits perfect. Only problem is the picture on the case peels quick. But still not bad for the money.
recomended it to my friends. was shipped properly, i intend to order more. even though it coming from far they deserve 5 stars. great product
I got this case for my wife's phone and she loved it. I gave it 4 stars only because of the limited color options. I could not get the color I wanted, just close enough to the color I want.

This case fit perfectly onto my android and has kept it from breaking.  I'm so glad that I purchased this item.  The color is a little darker than what it looks like online but it's still a good case.  I would purchase again from this vendor.
I loved this cover. The colors were perfect and it fit great.  I think I am going to order another one very soon.
For the price of $1.78 can't ask for too much but it's ok even though the little hook broke off same day I got it.
I loved the design, but it didn't my phone. The other cover I bought did, but, unfortunately, this one did not and it was my favorite
summary: I loved the design but it didn't my phone. The other cover I bought did, but not this one.

reviewText: Very nice case for someone who carries their phone in their pocket. Comes off very easy should the need arise and stays put like it should when in use. Gives the phone adequate cushion from short drops (less than 3ft.)I don't have any of the docks for my phone so I can't comment on fitment issues with the case on the phone. Although the case does come off easy so it would be a nice one to have should you have to take it off to mount in the dock.
summary: Great case, especially for the money

reviewText: Have you ever tried enlarging a picture and printing it out only to find its pixelated and blurry? That's exactly what this design looks like on my phone case.  You can barely read the text. I love the case itself but that's about it. It's a plain white case with no gloss to it that someone bought wholesale and printed on it with a cheap ink jet printer from 2001. Don't waste your $10 on this case, you seriously are paying for what kind of quality you want (or lack thereof).

I bought this case for my Motorola Atrix 4g because I enjoyed the aesthetics when looking for a case.  It's made of TPU so it's soft enough to sit in my pocket without digging into my leg, it's sturdy and has done it's job quite a few times (dropping onto the ground as I get out of the car) and done it well.However, these are the possible cons some might say.It gets hot! - duh, it's a case, of course it will trap more heat.It's too soft for me - Well, that's really up to the individual user to decide.I hate that it sticks to the original battery cover and comes off when I take off the case. - I don't see that as too much of a problem because it's just makes things easier for me to do a physical battery pull.In the end, I love the case, it protects the phone well with all that I do!

This is a really nice phone cover.  Only complaint is that it doesnt come off easy.  When my blackberry freezes up and needs to be reset I have a heck of a time removing this cover and once you get it off it doesnt quite fit as great as it did the first time but it does snap back on.  I get compliments all the time on how nice the phone looks.  Worth every penny.

I wanted something to protect my Atrix, distinguish mine from my husband's, and show up from across the room...this cover accomplishes those goals.  It is a little more transparent/less opaque than I though, but it looks good.

I have had this case for a few months now and it is still in great condition. I have dropped my phone and the case didn't break (neither did my phone)! I love the design, which shows no sign of fading. If and when I'm ready for another case I will definitely get another like it.

I tried three different times to get the item as listed here. Each time it was sent to me, the protector was more than an inch bigger than the phone it was supposed to be for. I finally just gave up on getting the product I needed.
The Screen Protector is not the right size. It's too big for the T-Mobile LG Optimus L9. Waste of money and time.
Rose Red????  When I got this item, I was shocked to find it was Hot Pink!!!!!The design was ok for a cheap case, but it was not the color it should have been!!!!
For the price it was a good item. Didn't expect it to be as nice as it was. So far it is holding up just fine.

I had seen this sort of case being offered by various brands, but decided to try out on this one. It looks rather nice, but it is not real leather here. I had accidentally dropped the iPhone once and it was able to protect it from being damaged or bruised. I was also able to access all buttons and switches easily with this case. In essence, it works well for me. Great value for money... I got the black one as well.
ITS CHEAPLY MADE AND THE TAB BROKE THE FIRST TIME I PUT IT ON MY PHONE. WASTED MONEY ON THIS
summary: BROKE THE FIRST TIME I PUT IT ON MY PHONE

reviewText: this case is really cute, but cheaply made. you can literally scratch off the design. mine case is almost completely white now with just the bow on it . it gets 2 stars because it's cute...
was cute kinda hard to put on but not so much once you get the hang of it lol very cute

At least the cleaning cloths are worth a few cents... these protectors have two small tabs- pull off the first, apply the protector to your iPhone, then pull off the second tab and you are finished. But the second tab will NOT come off, no matter what you do. This item was a complete waste of money.
I received the item in a short amount of time. The screen protectors are great, the lint cleaners are not the best but for the price they were, i cannot complain.
The product itself was great, very easy to apply and very very clear. Problem was there was only one protector and not three as was advertised.

I am pleasantly surprised with this item.  It was easy to install once I figured out the instructions (in English BUT still confusing).  I just assumed that it would be difficult to use the touch feature of the phone but does not hinder it at all.  Now I've only had it a few days but am pleased with it.  Kind of looks cool too when the phone goes blank it actually looks like a mirror.  I like it.....you get three for a very good price.  Even if I only leave it on for two months, I feel that it is definitely worth the price....and if it saves my screen from getting scratched, all the better.  One thing I really don't like is the little cloth that comes with it.  It isn't as nice as the one that came with my phone.  It isn't scratchy but feels a little rough to me. But all in all a good product.
What else can I say 3 screen protectors for this price, need I say more. Easy to apply.Say "poof" to the worries about scratching the iphone screen.
summary: Really 3 screen protectors for this price

reviewText: I bought one from "BlueHarborOnline" and it really disappointed me. The package is not like the one shown on the website. They sold you a cheap one. I saw some people wrote very good feedback and I think different seller is selling different products. And I am in bad luck to get a bad one! So many bubbles... Easily get scratches..! I throw three of them. Hope you are lucky and pick the seller who is selling the Crystal Clear thick Screen Protector but not this "p*l*a*s*t*i*c  w*r*a*p" :(

3 for the price of one. Not too bad. Shipping was a bit more to Alaska but everything is. Fit my new 3G just fine and now I have an extra for a friend. Has been a few weeks and still in place. I have another cover for outside the screen so that's probably helping. Each cover has its own cloth.
summary: Good deal. Did what it said it should.

reviewText: Doesn't work.  Find another product this one is VERY difficult to install and will tear and peel off easily. You get what you pay for.

I tried one other screen protector on the cheap, and I couldn't get it on correctly.  One try is all you get with some of these (yes i know the packaging has instructions, but seeing and doing is often very difficult, and I was being very careful).This product is nice because even if you are a klutz, you get two more tries to get it right.  The package comes with 3 of the included screen-thingys and also 3 polishing cloths.  The outside wrapper is very gaudy and super Japanese, but don't let looks deceive you. This screen protector applied very easily with holes cut out for the ear speaker and the home button. I had actually applied it slightly off center, and it actually allowed me to peel it right back off and put it right back on, no fuss or mess involved.  So I still have 2 extras.I have accumulated some gritty grime (very very minor) around the edges, and you can see the faint smudges of fingerprints when you hold it in the light, but this has not hindered perfect performance (and my rubber case hides everything but the screen anyway).Not much more I could say.  Quality performance in a screen protector, low low price, and you get 3 of them.  A good buy.
summary: Good price, 3 combo makes for good buy

reviewText: The product is cheap. But therein lies the problem. They seem to have used inferior materials for the product. You get what you pay for. The die cut is the exact size of the screen. It covers edge to edge and leaves absolutely no exposed areas. It is a bit difficult to get perfect alignment in application because there is zero leeway. But the biggest gripe I have is with the material. It scratches incredibly easily. If you are not 100 vigilant at all times, the material is scratched, I would say at least 10 times easier than the actual iPhone screen. I have used all three within a month. They were usually scratched with 1 hour of application.
It's an alright product... It's good enough to protect your iPhone but not the best.

These protectors are a bit more glossy than I was hoping for.  The three pack I ordered shipped with four - thanks! These were easy to apply, and made my wife's phone screen (which had small scratches in it) look much better with the screen applied.  Average product - properly fitted for i3G - no trimming.

The item comes in 3 individual packages. Comes with the screen protector and a small lint free cloth.The screen is not clear. Meaning, it has a matte finish to it which slightly distorts the picture. You see some prism effect from the light scattering off the screen protector. I didn't like the distortion because it felt like it was making the picture blurry and it gave me a headache.I eventually took it off because I didn't like the way it was distorting the screen.If you are looking for a matted screen protector, this is good for the price - but it wasn't for me. The shipping was prompt. I ordered it on July 3, 2009 and received it on July 9, 2009.I uploaded a picture of one of the packages and it should be in the gallery.
summary: Not 100% Clear, good for the price

reviewText: Purchased this product to protect the screen of 2 iPhones (a G3 and G3S). Instructions were clear and the protector is very forgiving of mistakes (allows you to reapply). Fits well over the screen with no major gaps. No noticeable decrease in screen sensitivity with protector in place. The protector does have a tendency to show finger smudges, however, this was only noticeable on indirect light (i.e. when using the phone in bright light) and cleans off fairly easily. Very clear when in darker surroundings. Overall, a nice screen protector.
summary: Good screen protector at great price.

reviewText: They are a great screen protectors for the money. The very first one went on with no troubles at all so you get the other two as basically extras! So you can save those and use them when the screen protector gets destroyed. The lint cloth is also pretty good and is a nice add on. Great screen guard highly recommended.

I've tried several other screen protectors for the iPhone, and this one is the by far the best! The screen protectors sold at the AT&T; store left a rainbow-looking residue along with bubbles (no matter how you applied the protector). These, though, were perfect! Very slick, glossy, and no bubbles whatsoever!You'd do yourself a favor to buy these and forgo the hassle of the more expensive and sub-par protectors out there.
...is because they are worthless. I used up all three of them immediately. Bubbles and rips. Complete garbage. [...]
summary: The reason why these are so cheap...

reviewText: Item arrived quickly and was just as described. Great screen protector for the money, went on easily and bubbles only took a few minutes to get out. Recommended for anyone with the iPhone 3g.

The package that you get is written in chinese, no english anywhere. When the screen protector was placed on the phone, the screen was not as clear as before it was put on. It almost appears that you should be able to peel off a film from the front to make the protector clear but after several attempts to do so, I ruined the protector. I do not support the purchase of this item. delivery was on time.
I've tried three different kinds of screen protectors and this one was by far the best! Barely visible, and mine lasted six months before even showing a scratch. Will definitely buy these again!

This screen protector is impossible to put on without a speck of dust and when you do get even one speck it creates a bubble on the screen that is impossible to iron out. After deciding I would live with a little bubble the edges started peeling off and more bubbles appeared making it unattractive and annoying. I would not buy this screen protector again as my last generation iphone screen protector was excellent so I know a better one exists (I wish I could remember the name!)
summary: Edges peel off quickly and it's impossible to avoid bubbles

reviewText: I'm wondering if all these screen protectors are actually the same.  Others have complained of bubbles and fingerprints while mine is just about perfect.  After almost 2 weeks I have only had to wipe the fingerprints off a couple of times and it's even hard to tell there's a protector on it at all.  For the value of about $1/protector(with shipping) it's hard to beat this.The orginal protector that came with my case was much worse than this.  It was a grease magnet with bubbles everywhere.
summary: This is a great screen protector

reviewText: Don't work great with wrap around cases. Any push to the edge causes bubbles but product does just what it was designed for

It's not like I could expect much from a $1 screen protector but I thought it could at least be usable. After taking the screen protectors out of the packaging, I tried to apply them to my iPhone 3G. I had to peel it off because there were literally THOUSANDS of bubbles that were impossible to remove--believe me I tried. I reapplied the protectors many many times and ended up using up all three screen protectors in the process of trying to get one to stick correctly to the iphone. The screen protectors are soft--like plastic wrap, not hard at all--so don't expect it to just smoothly stick onto the phone without catching air bubbles. Besides the bubbles, the protector makes the phone screen look greasy and just bad. They also got scratched horribly when I tried to put on my iPhone protector case, so I ended up throwing all three of the screen protectors away. Putting plastic wrap over my phone probably would have had better results. The only item that was worth anything was the lint cleaning cloth.I don't think the other reviewers who gave this high star ratings are talking about the same protectors that I got, seeing as how theirs seem to have worked, and without bubbles. I got mines at this site but from the seller Blue Harbor, so DON'T buy it from that seller.
3rd protector I've tried for my iPhone. Worst one by far. Makes the screen look horrible.

I bought these covers for the price.Obviously I was wrong. Although installation was very easy ( you can peel off and re-apply if bubbles appear) the cover scrached as soon as I put it on. I am very careful with my phone, but after 2 weeks of use the screen protector was scrached so badly that i could hardly see the screen. I then installed the second one with a new case that partially covers the screen, and after 2 days the screen is already showing noticible scraches. I have not this problem with any of my other covers.I would not suggest this product to anyone.

these films are just a nanometer too big at the corners.  if you have a hard shell type case on your iphone it grabs the film when you slide the case on and you end up with big bubbles at the corners.  also, the films they sent me had a reflective mirror finish instead of clear.  nowhere in the description did it mention that, so it was probably just a mis-ship; but at less than 3 dollars there is no point in sending them back.  i ended up throwing all three cover films away after spending many fruitless hours trying to cut them down to size.  these things suck!  don't waste your time or money.
Love my cover for my iPhone just as cute as my little kitty Boo. Now I can take a reminder of her everywhere with my phone.
Very cute item.  The cat is more brown but I still liked it.  The case holds up very well.  I have dropped my phone alot and it hasn't broken the case yet.

This screen protector is the best of all I have used till now...I dont know why people are giving low ratings...I have been using this for more than 5 months and haven't changed the screen till now. Go get it, what i would recommend to everyone out there.Pradp

What that means is that everyone who has actually bought and used this product thinks that it is crap. Furthermore, many of the reviewers have posted twice on this product, once per color. It does have drivers on it, but not for this phone.The "Bonus" CD contains a vast amount of pictures that is XXX-RATED. reviewText: Nothing wrong with the quality of materials of these protectors, but the buyer should be aware that they are UNIVERSAL, which means they are a generic size, and must be cut to fit the Touch's screen.The HTC Touch, or Elf, has a screen with rounded edges, and unless you are very talented, or into scrapbooking, you are going to end up with less than a perfect fit, which may not be satisfactory to many users.The description of this item should read "universal" first, and "can be used with wireless phones such as the HTC Touch", second. I bought them unaware of what I was really getting.I will say that the vendor, A Days Tech, was very fair and offered to take the protectors back and give a full refund, or let me keep them with a partial credit. I kept them, since they can be used for any electronics with a screen, in a pinch. Kudos to the vendor for making sure I was happy.
summary: Note: this is a UNIVERSAL protector, not custom fitted to Touch

I was looking for a case for my Samsung Epic that was stylish and didn't ass to much bulk to my phone. There really isn't that much offered out right now. The case itself had a rubber like coating on the outside, it felt OK and offered a better grip over the feel of the normal phone. It didn't add to much bulk to the phone. The things I didn't like is that though the outside of the case was coated in a black the inside of the case was gray and not coated at all, when the phone is placed into the case you can definitely see the gray borders which makes the phone look cheap. The case slides onto the phone so it's not as secure as I would like. The build quality of the case make it so it doesn't aligned perfectly with the front and back bezels. The bezels have a bit of extra edge to them, this hinders the sliding mechanism of the Epic. All the correct cut outs for the phone are present, so that part is good. Overall I would not recommend buying this product, better to invest the money you were going to spend on this towards a more expensive better build case.

This cover is mildly rubberized which can be both a plus and a minus -- there was a tiny bit of drag as I would slide it into my side pocket, but that same rubberized feature also kept it from sliding out of my side pocket when I'd sit down. reviewText: I took a chance on this case given there were no reviews.  The case fits my EVO very snug, it snaps tight around it and appears to be secure.  The case itself is a clear plastic which has been painted silver on the inside and the design printed on the out, which gives it the appearance of hovering over the silver.  Everything is accessible with the case on.  The case sticks out far enough in back so that when my phone is set down on the back, the camera's lens does not touch the table - this was one of my big reasons for buying a case.It has that rubberized plastic feel, so its easy to grip, but not sticky.  The downside of this case is three things: when you look at the back you can see outlines in the silver paint where the mold has a seam where each of the plastic tabs holding it together are, they are like faint squares underneath and at the edges you can make out the tabs. Because of the busy design its not like this is all you see, but its very visible if you look at the case.  This is because the surface of the inside of the case has these in it, and since the case is painted from the inside they are visible. Second, the design does not wrap, the wrong part of the case is made with the exact design as the back side, so that the kind of "9" piece is on the side of the front of the case on the right side of the phone. This means that the design seams at the side, rather than wrapping around.  Third, and most importantly, the seams at the sides of the case just make the case look cheap. They are slightly raised and are not at all invisible.  I think if the company had taken the time to smooth the seams before painting the case, it would look much better. You can't of course try to do that yourself because you would just wear off the design and make it look worse.That said, the case is less than ten dollars, so I'm not expecting perfection here.  The case fits well and will do its job for the time being I am planning to use it.Update: Changing to 1 star - Have had the case 2 weeks, the pattern and texture are now flaking off.  I'm going to buy a new case, as this one is just crap.
summary: Pretty design, fits snug, but cheap craftmanship

reviewText: Purchased these for my wife - great quality build, fast shipping.  These look even nicer in person.  The print is slightly darker than the picture shown on amazon.  Stays on the phone and have already helped save the phone from a fall.
This phone is even cuter in person. It works perfectly. I couldn't have asked for a better phone. On top of that, it is smooth and silky to the touch.
I love this.  Very classy and pretty.  It holds up well too.  Last 2 I ordered broke right away, one while putting it on.  I am very happy with this.

I wished this had worked out better. The cover never really fit the phone and kept falling off. We never got the top part to stay on at all and I told my daughter to at least use the bottom part which would be better protection than none. Within a week the the flower design was peeling off the cover. Within two weeks part of the cover broke off. I realize this was in the hands of a teenage girl but wasn't that why I was buying a hard cover in the first place? Unfortunatly, I have never been able to find a cover for her phone in a store or at the mall in one of those vendors, where we could try it on before purchasing.  Now I am stuck with trying to purchase a new one on-line and hoping for better results and making sure the teen does not throw away return papers again this time.
When you first see and.install it all looks really good.  However the first drop of the phone resulted in the case breaking and now is no longer usable.
I liked the style of the cover a lot but the production was not that great. I only had for a couple of weeks and it is already falling apart. The clasps that hold the cover on are already breaking.

This phone case is very beautiful, but the front of the case does not stay on the phone at all. As soon as I pick my phone up it is falling off. Would not recommend this case, I would recommend a rubber case.
I really liked this cover when I received. Sadly, the front part broke very easily...within the first week. The clips attaching it to the phone aren't well made. The back stays on great.
summary: Too bad it broke so quickly.

reviewText: The carbon fiber hard cover protecter is very nice for the price.  Works well with the kickstand when leaving it on the table to watch videos.  For those who likes to leave their phone in their pocket, the rubber on the cover doesn't create any friction so your phone should slide nicely into your pockets, especially if you wear jeans.  The right side of the hard covers feel a little bit loose like it's not holding together tightly but that is a minor thing to me.  Unfortunately, I've only had it for a few weeks because I accidently dropped my phone from three feet and it landed on a cornder.  The corner broke and now the case is useless to me.  This is a nice cover as long as you don't drop it on a hard surface since the plastic is relitively cheap.The screen protector and the belt clip I didn't get to use because I generally like to keep my phone in my pocket and plus I already had a screen protecter on my phone so I'm saving this one up when I need to replace it.Overall I think this is a nice cover but the cheap plastic that it is made of is the biggest draw back when it comes to accidental drops.
summary: Nice rubberized cover as long as you don't drop it.

reviewText: I purchased three different cell phone cover faceplates at the same time; all of them were exactly like the photos and descriptions given. I always look for a faceplate with a unique design but that also has a rubberized feel. This vendor has a big selection for my phone, which is why I purchased three... couldn't make up my mind. :)
This case is cheap and will not last. The plastic tabs that are meant to keep it in place break off and the case will no longer stay on my wifes phone. What a colossal waste of money, don't buy it!
I loved the way this looked on the computer, but when i got it in the mail, it kinda looked cheap.  the face plate tabs broke in a month so I can no longer use it.  But looks decent from far away.
This was really cute and functional, but cheaply made. Only use for a couple weeks before the tabs broke up and it would no longer stay on the phone.

I purchased this phone case for my daughter. As soon as she tried putting it on, both hinges on one side of the front cover snapped off, rendering the piece useless. This product would not deserve a one star rating were it not for the blatant negligence of their customer service. I emailed them requesting they address my dissatisfaction over a week ago, and they still have refused to respond. "Handheldfashion" does not stand behind the quality of their products. I'd advise you put your money elsewhere.

I loved this case when I got it! I was pretty impressed because the color didn't rub off like my hard case did.  I was very disappointed though when the tabs on the face plate broke and I couldn't use it anymore. Feel kinda let down :(

Because this phone model can no longer be purchased I was afraid that I would not find a case for it. Amazon to the rescue again!!! The case was delivered promptly and it fit the phone perfectly. Thanks Again!

I bought this case several months ago and I love it! It snapped easily onto my phone (the Samsung Realty) and has protected it nicely ever since.  I have also taken it off and put it back on several times with no trouble.  The screen protector (which has a matte finish but is easy to see through) was not difficult to apply and has prevented me from scratching my screen.  My phone is red, so the case matches it nicely.  I like the design, and have received several compliments on it.  One of the reasons I chose this phone was its small size, so I was worried the case would make it bulky, but the case barely changes the phone's size.  I highly recommend it.
The only problem with this was my daughter kept taking it off and putting it back on... after a couple of times, it broke.  Great case... but leave it on.

I got this phone case, and it looked very nice, but it only lasted me for 2 weeks. I dropped my phone 3 times and the case cracked and eventually split. Very cheap, but I should've expected that out of an inexpensive phone case.
Within a day all for clips that hold the cover together had broke. I have purchased covers through Amazon before and have not had any problems with them.
The art on the case is great. The only problem I have with it is the fact that it broke. I have had it for less than a month, and the front cover has already broken.

A friend picked this out and it was ordered as a gift.  Product has nice design and pricing.  It may not be a perfect fit.  Friend says that the faceplate keeps coming off.  The grips may have broken or do not snap securely.

I bought this item for my husband to protect his phone from dents & scratches.  He liked the design, but the little plastic tabs that hold the front cover on broke within the first month. The back cover is still holding on fine.  I guess these are not made to last forever thats why they are so cheap.
This is a very cool snap on cover , bought it for my grandson who , took if off one to many times and broke the clips on the edge! If you buy one ,leave it on, and when you take it off , be CAREFULL

Really cute rainbow rhinestone hard cover for the Samsung Impression phone.  My daughter loves it and gets lots of compliments.  She's dropped it a couple of times and it protects the phone well!  Just what I wanted it for!

This phone case consists of 2 pieces - one to cover the top sliding part of the phone, and one to cover the back part of the phone. The top part was so flimsy and thin that the tiny pieces that keep it on the phone broke within a couple days. The back part is great but I no longer have a top part. Not worth 10 bucks.

The rubberized feel of these covers are nice and they fit very well on the phone. The print on the back is almost impossible to see. You may as well get plain black. You will also want to use a black marker on the inside rim of the covers to hide the white when you slide your phone open.

I was very satisfied with the promptness in receiving my order. However I did not receive my belt clip, and I feel the description of the color ahould be changed from white red flower to grey red flower. I really wanted white.

I ordered this cover and they sent me the wrong color. I kept the cover however I wouldn't recommend it, it broke the second week I had it. Right near the corner. You must handle it delicately, I purchased it as a package with the screen guard. The screen guard worked well as long as you know what your doing when applying it.
First one that arrived was broken. The replacement didn't last long. I dropped it in my house and it broke quite easily. Very disappointed.
My wife like it, we ended up not using it becouse I got her a bigger battery that came with it's own cover.

took a while to get to me its really cute just hard to come off which is good and bad i guess good because its secure if you drop the phone and bad because you may have to use something to get it open to clean or switch cases in any event i like its hard rubber and design
this case is just as pretty and nice as the picture. its real sturdy which is good because i drop my phone a lot.
I bought this item 7 months ago.  It is still holding up well, some of the graphics are very finely wearing off.  This is a great inexpensive way to customize and protect your phone.

I got this case in today. I love the look, colors, and it fits perfect.... It got here faster then I expected also. Love it....It didn't however come with the belt clip that it had said, but I wouldnt of used it anyways. :)
Very nice cover fits great.  Like the outer jell, color is just like the picture.  Would buy more from.  Thank you for a very good item.
This product arrived on time and at the right price.The easy grip surface keeps one from dropping it.The ease of installation had my phone looking cool in minutes.
summary: Black skull phone cover is coool

reviewText: This product design is great, exactly what I saw on my computer screen. It is great that it fits and stays, however when you are having battery issues and need to take the battery out, this product is very hard to take off. When I say hard, I mean nearly impossible with the bare hands to take off! If you plan on never removing this product or using something like a knife (which I had to wedge in the middle to get it off-which ended up bending the material) then this product is for you!

Wanted this for my phone and when it arrived it all looked good. When I put it on my phone case it keep falling off.  You had to be so careful with it bc anything part of the sticker sticking out whould pull it off.  I thought I would have been a little better then what I thought.
summary: Didn't stick the way it should

reviewText: Like the title said, cute. But it didn't last long. The few times I dropped my phone with this case on has scuffed it and finally broken it. I didn't drop the phone hard or anything either. The corners that snap this onto your phone are what broke. The little lip that sticks out to secure it on snapped off in multiple places.It did look very cute and layered with the pattern, though. It also had a very nice silky rubber/plastic feel to it. But deff not durable.

i bought this case for my black berry the supplier sent the wrong case design but it was no problem, i e mailed them they immediately sent the correct one and i even got to keep the wrong one, great service. Will recommend this supplier to any one. it is a clean clear design ........nice.

I also purchased this for my daughters phone. It fit the phone well, was not too bulky and looked good.But within 30 days, the case cracked from normal use (it was not dropped) and is now no longer useable.
This is my third cover. They fit perfectly on my phone and really helps when picking it up. It gives me more "grip" when it has a cover on it. These covers are a great price and I recommend them.

Bought this for my 16 yo son. I should start off with how much he loved this case. Aesthetically, he loved it so much we have purchased several. Several because they broke every third time he dropped his phone. So while it looks great it wasn't much for protection and will not withstand a clumsy 16 yo boy. Luckily its pretty cheap price wise. We paid about 4 bucks for it I think.

I really liked this case, the design is awesome and it fitted my phone very well. Notice I used past tense in the previous line. For me the case only lasted about a month because I was clumsy and dropped it. I've purchased many cases for this type of phone and I have yet to come across a case that doesn't break very easily. The case will do it's job and keep it from getting scratched or chipped. This case is not heavy duty so if you are one of those people that drops things constantly, this is not for you. However if you are looking for a fashionable, cheap, and effective way to protect your phone, this case will do just fine.
I've always had plain solid colors, but when I saw this I thought it would look nice.  It is great.  Stays on good and it is very pretty.  I would recommend this to anyone who need a good cover.

I BOUGHT THIS COVER FOR MY DAUGHTER'S PHONE IN SEPTEMBER AND BY OCTOBER THE COVER KEPT FALLING OFF.  THE PRODUCT WAS QUITE FLIMSY AND KEPT POPPING OFF THE PHONE.  AFTER A`WHILE IT EVENTUALLY CRACKED AND COULD NOT BE USED ANYMORE.  ONLY THING NICE ABOUT THIS ITEM IS THE ARRAY OF COLORS.  DON'T WASTE YOUR MONEY ON THIS CRAP!!!!
This is my second cover for my phone and this one is very pretty. Reminds me of Hawaiian flowers. The colors are very pretty.
Purchased this to protect my cell phone Pantech Ease P2020, was very easy to put on and is what the description and picture stated, very satisfied

Good service, quick shipping, product as described. Love the design! My only complaint is that it makes it a bit difficult to slide the phone open. Still worth the price though, and it seems to be improving over time.
I bought this phone case for my daughter and it lasted her 7 months. She absolutely loved it and she dropped it so many times and it didn't even break. It protected her phone very much.

A beautiful rubberized pantech ease AT&T phone case that fits the phone perfectly and comes with a static cling faceplate cover.A great buy as it does not slip out of your hand and has an awesome vivid design.

Was thrilled to see the coloring and design of this case. A beautiful navy back ground with colored flower design. The delivery was fast and product very well wrapped. The fit was simple just snapped on and looks great! The rubberized case feels great and a no slip texture is a plus! Yes, I would recommend this product and company.

My wife purchased this for her phone.  It fits the phone perfect and looks great!  The quality of the product is well beyond the asking price.  I would recommend this product to anyone that has this phone and likes the skin.
Beautiful and fits well. The price was good, and the cover has a great rubbery (rather than hard and brittle) feel.
Liked it for several months, after awhile the picture wore away and didn't look as nice.  It broke about 6 months after buying it.  For the cheap price I guess it's ok.
summary: looked great in beginning, 6 months later broke

reviewText: Timely shipping on behalf of the seller. Dropped phone once and front plate broke beyond use. Pattern is already chipping off of the phone. Was very happy with product but only for the first couple of weeks. I have had this problem with other brands of plates for this phone, not a good phone to get snap on's for.
Looks just like the picture, but more pretty then the picture.  I LOVE IT.  Wish it came in more colors.
1.)Its Green2.)It's Green3.)It's Green4.)It's Green5.)It's Green6.)It's Green7.)It's Green8.)It's Green9.)It's Green10.)It has flowers
summary: 10 Reasons Why I Love my phone case

reviewText: Awesome case, has been in and out of pockets and bags and still looks great.  Doesn't interfere with phone operation.  Arrived promptly, packaged as promised.
Versatile and pretty and I purchased this and the other together for my daughter as a set. I am not sure that I would have if she wasn't standing right by me.
This phone cover is really colorful and it is not made cheap.I am very pleased with this phone cover. Fast delivery too.

My girlfriend ordered this for her Epic 4g after getting one of those gelled cases. This fits the phone perfect and almost has a 3-dimensional design because the print sits on top of the item with the case being kind of frosted black plastic. The feel of it is good in the hand and doesn't slip around when grasping it. It won't offer any protection if you drop the phone with this case but it is slightly raised from the screen. I prefer the rubber cases for my phone but this works for what she does.
Definitely best case ive ever had. Has some sort of slip grip which is great! Looks really cute! Easy to put on and take off too!
Love this, I have gotten so many compliments on the case. It came quickly and is as promised. Thanks!! I will definitely purchase again.

I had this case before but it broke so I ordered another one.  The case came packaged securely.  I love the rubberized case because it doesn't make the phone too bulky as other plastic cases do.  I ordered this case because the picture says its "black" but instead I got the same case in silver with black flowers.  I would recommend if you looking for a simple case that will protect your phone while still making it look nice.

This case snaps right on and hasnt fallen off once. It's also a very nice design... it is starting to lose some of the paint a little but nothing too serious (after about 3 weeks)... for me, it makes using the touch screen a little difficult close to the sides because the cover gets in the way of my finger. I have gotten used to it a little but i would still probably take it off if it wasn't so cute.

The case came very quickly, however, the front plate was broken so I had to use a black front case from another set that I had.  I did not attempt to send it back or anything although I would like another front case.
summary: I got half of what I paid for.

reviewText: As the previous reviewer stated, the design looks great! It looks layered which doesn't come across in the pictures. The feel of it is nice, it doesn't stick to your hands the way some of the rubberized ones do. My only complaint is the amount of bulk it adds to the phone, it makes it significantly bigger.

I purposefully searched for a case that would cover more of the faceplate without just being a rim around the edge. My friend had a case that only clipped around the edge, he was frustrated and took it off because it kept popping off. The next day, he dropped his phone and cracked the screen. I like that it is girlie...when I first bought this phone, it was difficult to find anything but basic black. It has done a very decent job protecting my phone. My only disappointment is that the black is a coating and if you drop you phone on accident, it scrapes off the black and it starts to flake.

I received this in mail 2 days after I ordered. Was very impressed with the protective screen cover that came with it, easy to put on and good quality. The cover looks just like the picture. Would recommend this.

Well immediately out of the box I was taken-aback by the lack of quality in the appearance of the case.  I really liked the design so I decided to play it to the side as long as no rhinestones came off.(Side note the rhinestones are black not clear tinted black}  Well guess what happened day One stones around the edge and seams started to come off and continue to come off at day 4.  Also the case is very hard to take apart.  At this point I am afraid to put the screen protector on.

There is NO problem at all with this cover scraping against the keyboard. The other reviewers obviously installed the front cover on upside down. The front cover has two small latches on one of the long-sides of the cover. These latches are to grab a hold of the phone. The other long-side of the cover has no latches at all (this side is supposed to be on the keyboard side). However, if you install the cover upside down, the latches will be on the keyboard side and rub up against your keys. Simply purchase and install in the correct orientation and the cover works great!
bought a phone case to protect my phone, phone still broke, had to buy the evo instead because i didnt buy the warranty. case is usless, but pretty.
I won't buy again. It doesn't come looking as nice as the pictures and the rubber starts peeling instantly leaving you with an ugly hard case with white chunks. Horrible
This cover looks good, fits well but is not durable.  The seller is excellent, but the product falls apart with normal use and after two of them, we will look for something else.

My girlfriend bought several cases online for her HTC Samsung Smartphone.  She changes them every week for a different look, so expect many more in the future.  We also have interest in a Rubber Case for this exact phone.  Rubber Phone Case so if you drop it you won't crack it!!!  If someone could email me back with any suggestions, we will order one or more.

Literally just got this 10 minutes before I wrote this but the case fits perfectly and looks pretty ill, a bit feminine maybe. Regardless, the case is cool but in terms of durability, I'll have to find out.
I was greatly disappointed with the quality of the cell phone cover.  The workmanship was aweful.
The case cracked within first week of use. Very cheap but you get what you pay for

I was disappointed with the quality of this item. The shipping took longerThan the quoted amount of time- My son likes the cover, so I kept he item - However....If it had. Een for myself, I would have returned it:-( Overall, I could have purchased this qualityAt the local " Dollar Store"
It kept falling off of my phone. But it was quite a beautiful phone case. I simply would not purchase one like it again.
The first day I used the case it just fell off the couch onto carpet, and it cracked. Not only that but it's already chipping the paint, and I've only had it for a week or so.
Cover fits well.  The plaid is nothing close to what is shown.  My cover is mostly brown with a green stripe (does blue and brown make green?). Disappointed.
The case fits the phone nicely but the color is more teal and brown, rather than black and blue. The deliverey time was very quick.

Since the phone that I have is pretty much outdated it was difficult to find a nice case for it. I settled on purchasing this one. It is almost exactly as pictured. It is teal with lots of brown/gray tones. The only difference I found was the photo did not show the back of the case having a place for a detachable holster. I thought I was just purchasing a case, didn't really need the holster part so it just has a hole in the back. Around the edges of the case where there is no plastic coating, you can see the faded area of the coloring. It doesn't bother me too much but just an FYI to other buyers. There isn't much selection out here for the Env2 phones, so if you really need a case this one works. It does feel pretty durable unless you drop it but at least it feels strong enough to protect the phone.
summary: Good Case For An Old Phone

reviewText: The cover was trendy and I received it quick. It's hard to get off the phone. I feel like its going to break sometimes.
Very nice product. Received on time. Easy to use, even for me! And it stays clean looking. And it's the exact hot pink color I wanted! Awesome!
summary: Hot Pink Rubberized Snap on Skin for Samsung Instinct

reviewText: The case is just a simple snap on case. It has the hole in the back to hook to a belt clip. It worked just as expected!
This is a great, cheap cover if you like the rubberized feel with the durability of a plastic case.
It is more silver, than white.  It is also a little big and drags the keys when you slide it open.  Got it for my daughter, and I am afraid she is going to tear up the phone with it

my daughter loves this phone cover case alot.  she comments on it almost everyday how she loves it.  the colorful look, the way it feels, she can grip it well in her hand and wont slide out.  this was a good buy for her, practical and inexpensive too.

Ordered this cover for my, high school age, daughter.  She loved it.  The cover has a pearlized finish that makes it look even nicer than the picture.  Her friends went crazy over the cover. The only thing we could have lived without is the cut out on the back for a belt clip (ugh).

Cannot beat this product for the price.  The first one ordered was damaged upon arrival. Sent an eMail with attached picture of the damaged item and a new one arrived within a week.  Graet service and price!

The major problem I have with this product is when I put it on my phone the phone does not work. By it being a touch screen phone when something is touching it you can't press any buttons. The case fits so tight around the phone it causes it to touch the screen and the phone thinks someone is touching it. Needless to say I threw the case away the first day I received it.

Of course, with any item under a dollar, you expect that things may go wrong for it to be so affordable. You would be right in this case. (Pardon the Pun) If I can say anything, it is that in America today, you get exactly what you pay for. Nothing more, nothing less. Try and spend a few dollars to get it right the first time, and don't be a cheap skate like me. The case has cracked, and is now not even holding together, with little to no physical demand being put on the phone itself, the case has acted as if it were put through an obstacle course.

Its a OK case for under a buck! Others said the case comes apart, mine is stuck together very good! As for putting the clip on it pretty simple, just stick the sticker on the little screw and onto the back of the case, put the case on and screw the clip on! However I did break the clip very easily, because I didn't know to press the button to get phone on and off! Works just as good without the clip unless that's why you want this one and I think that I just broke the clip and its not defective! Its protected my phone very well for about a year now and I'm a 23 year old male who works in a warehouse and has dropped it from about 40 feet in the air before! That's just my view on this! I just bought 2 more!!

Holds on to the cell phone very well, no issues with it so far. I am not using the belt clip because my phone is carried in my purse or carry bag to work. I would get more of these in the future. Helps protect my phone from scratches and if its dropped.

I didn't like the quality of this product. The kick stand pops out by itself whenever ti gets a chance. Also the axle pin pops out 1/3rd of the way from the kick stand. You would have to push the pin in first before closing the stand. It kept me busy :-I ended up returning mine. May be just a bad piece.
summary: Poor Quality, Kick Stand Pops Out, Pin Pops Out

reviewText: The product is listed as having a clip...it didn't say that it came dissasembled and you had to figure out how to put it together...by the way..I never did! The texture of the case is awesome, although it is a hard case it has a rubber feel to it.  Issue with the case itself is that if you bump it or drop it, it comes apart.  I purchased this as protection to my phone because of how often I dropped it and so far everytime I drop it the case comes off.  I guess it is true, you absolutely get exactly what you pay for!!!

All of the 10 skins my wife and I bought this is my favorite and most used one. I love this thing. I love the way it feels the way it fits and expespecialy the way it looks. Great product I wouldn't change a thing If you like the design buy it IT LOOKS EVEN BETTER IN PERSON!!!"
The price was right, fast delivery, product looked as I imagined. Did last more than a week, crumbling to pieces. Funny thing ...it was never dropped.  Two thumbs down for this one.

I loved this case as soon as I saw it! But it didn't fit my phone exactly right, however the company I bought it from has been so kind & helpful in taking it back and sending me a new one I highly recommend buying from this distributor!

It's pretty, but... its bulky. the decorated bling bling thingies start popping off and the case starts looking like a bad case of scabies. the bulky design makes it difficult to get a secure contact between my finger and the screen. would be ok for a non touch screen phone. or one where there are no control icons on the bottom or top half of the phone. I am waiting on my second choice to arrive. i did not return this product. its trash
This product shipped very fast as well as have a very long life to it. it did not chip and it really protects your phone when it drops.

The colors don't look as nice as that picture. I felt uncomfortable even putting this case on my Galaxy because it is made of a hard plastic that isn't completely smooth and could scratch it. The rhinestones fell off really easily. I don't even think I ever used this case, because it sucked so bad. Pretty disappointing.
Love the caseLove the screen protectorsLove the tool to get the case offLOVE THIS CASE (:
Love my new cell phone protector.  It looks very classy and protects my phone.  Very easy to attach to phone.I received the product within a week after I ordered.  Great product!
The design is really nice, and the texture is really cool (even though its flat) but it doesnt leave much room for the USB, and you can not get the damn thing off!
summary: This Sucker Is Really On There!

reviewText: nice case, great fit - but in a short time several of the rhinestones fell off.  not a huge problem, i can probably just buy rhinestones and glue them back on - but the original look of the case was awesome - its not that obvious that rhinestones are missing.  good buy - it makes me smile.
summary: great fit, cute - may not last too long, though

reviewText: The item came and was visually really nice. I snapped it on my phone and the plastic was very thin and cheap. It cracked shortly after putting it on and now it has broken in three places and is unusable. The felt bag that came with it was nice to put my phone in so I can put it in my purse that way.Would not recommend this product. I bought a different case for the same price from a different seller and it's much thicker and more durable. No problems with that one at all!
The beads are not shiny and don't look very elegant.  Looks very cheap. The plastic on which the stones are based is rough and grainy
I had this for about a week stones started to fall out. I did not drop it or anything. I love the cover but the stones do not last long....

Well, after much debating over different covers, this one seemed the one that I would go with with its unique earthy desgin and white background. However, after receiving it, it was a shiny coat of plastic grey with a rubberized coat on it with the imprint on that. The price was too pricy for what I thought it was which was a semi metal like material with a small rubberized layer and white undercoat. The design I believed would be underneath as well.  Youd do get a clip ( a little large for my case) and a simple rubberized bracelet. The total cost of shipping and the object was around 10 bucks. I would only buy this product again if it was really really something I wanted.
summary: Super Fast Shipping, Not exactly as seen in picture!

reviewText: I received the item in a timely manner. There were a couple of beads missing and I did not receive the flannel bag as promised. I will probably order other items but not the beaded ones. Maybe because of the fragile product a few loose beads should be given for replacements.
I loved it it fits perfect. No way dropping my phone and damaging it. I'm. I'm very pleased and it looks good. Had no problem with it keeps my phone secure.
Constantly receiving compliments on this case. It fits well and it comes with bonus cleaning cloth and case. I would recommend to others.
summary: Always complimented. Fits and works well.

reviewText: It is firm but rubbery and protective. The design is wearing off slightly at the edges leaving a clear edge. Hopefully this will not all wear off as it did on the White Flowers design case. Fits great, charger goes in well.
It protects my phone and is very pretty.  It is easy to put on and remove..  It accomplishes everything I wanted.
summary: I am very happy with the case

reviewText: Exactly as described but also works perfectly with my AT&T Galaxy S II i777!!! Has a nice smooth finish and protects the phone VERY well!!!!
compre este Case hace varios meses y protege el celular de manera excelente..ni siquiera tube que comprar protector de pantalla y gracias a dios mi cel este nuevo..

reviewText: OEM PLANET PRODUCTS ARE GOOD.I love the product.Its more than i expect.Worth for money.Thanks amazon for such good product marketing.
I have just received the case and started using... This case really fits the phone and durable and it is black my color ;-) I recommend everyone who has Samsung Galaxy SII
summary: Really good case for Samsung Galaxy SII

reviewText: Unfortunately this case did not fit my Samsung Galaxy S2, the adaptor holes and camera holes were not lined up properly.  It was like it was upside down.  Bummer, because I loved the case itself.  This seller was great to refund my cost for the case without shipping it back to them.

I was looking for a case for my new Galaxy S2 (At&t version). The store was selling similar cases for $20 and $35. I just can't justify spending that much on a case. reviewText: If you own a Samsung Galaxy SII you will definite appreciate this case. It fits perfectly on your phone, matching all the cut outs, and good protection all around.
This rubber case is worth its money.  Fit extremely well.  One heck of a bargain and would buy it again.
It adds pretty significant weight to the light-weighted Samsung GS2. Overall this is an OK case, nothing fancy. I guess you get what you paid for.....

Overall, the product is sleek and black enough to pass my expectations on how a black case should look. It doesn't quite fit that snug- the material bends on the upper and lower borders of the case so that it doesn't quite cover the borders entirely. Also, there's a hole in the upper right-hand corner of the case. I thought that the bumper would prevent the phone from getting scratched, but I tested it by rolling that corner on my desk and there is a possibility that the phone could get dented. This is a strange design because we buy cases so that the phone will not get scratched, and why should we pay for something that has a hole in it that will not protect the phone? However, comparing the price of this case and prices of other cases it is a risk that I'm going to take.
summary: Random Hole in the Upper Right-Hand Corner of the Case

reviewText: I liked the case, and for the amount of money paid, its a good buy, i personally like stronger cases, this is very flexible and indeed looks like a hard case, a little bit of more firmness wouldnt hurt.Protects VERY well the phone as well as the camera lens there is not one single part of the phone touching the surface of the table when i leave it there. Very Good purchase.

reviewText: Did not expect much but its cheap and works great! Only gripe the volume cutout was not opened and had to cutout myself...but it was easy. Also some openings needed shaving from the injection mold to get a clean edge look.The case is a hard urethane plastic like a rollerblade wheel. It has the same tackiness too even with a shiny surface but slides easily in the pocket. If placed on a car console its plastic tackiness grips so it does not slide or collect lint. Its shiny so it does show some fingerprints but cleans easily.Overall up close critical eye...a cheap looking case but everyone commented the case looks great from a distance, nice and shiny can't see the edges, does not add any bulkiness to phone and can get to all the openings needed plus a very tight fit w/no looseness around the edges. Only time will tell if it lasts awhile but for the price can buy another to replace if needed.

I think you cant get a better cover in this price from any other place apart from Amazon or from any other website. Fits the mobile perfectly well and protects the mobile from scratches on the back as well as front side. Must buy if you have a galaxy S2.

It don't see it as the case's fault though, there's simply not enough room to make the hole bigger.

The vendors should make things as clear as possible, given that one "S2 case/phone" is different from another.Upgrading the review to four stars, since the case is fine, just for the wrong phone. Overall this case is a basic rubberized case.  Nothing special to it, and it fits pretty well on my AT&T; i777 SGS2.There are a few things that I see that are not perfect, but because of the price I still give it 4 stars.Fit: The overall fit is pretty tight.  The buttons line up and are not too difficult to press, however the power button does feel that I have to give it a decent push to have it react.The lip that wraps to the front face doesn't quite wrap completely onto the front, on the bottom edge I can see the silver of the case edge, but around the top I do not.  It is almost as though it is not quite deep enough to wrap fully around it.  It does however fit tight enough that it won't fall or slip off the phone.I also found that the USB cutout is a bit off center.  This doesn't effect the connection of the cable I have (which is pretty skinny around the connector), however it would interfere with a larger cable end.The protection is something, but doesn't feel that it is a lot.  The rubber is a bit stiff and I wonder if it was dropped how much it would absorb.  It would however protect it from marks or scrapes because it does wrap completely around the face with a small lip.For the price this gives you the basic protection, without being too big or pricey.  I think that this is a good alternative to someone that likes the smaller phone, but does want something on it.

In fact the case LOOKS thicker than it is because the edging on the front protrudes out from the screen more so than most hard-plastic cases. This could be a good thing though as it will keep the screen well away from the surface it's laying on. The camera is also sufficiently protected. I like how the material wraps the entire phone, protecting all edges of the device. The rubberized material feels good in hand and has good fitment, my phone feels SAFE in this case.At it's price, I would highly recommend this case even if you are looking at others. I bought this case for my AT&T; Galaxy S2.  The case fit almost perfectly.  As others have mentioned, I had to make a new hole on the top since the noise cancelling microphone was moved slightly for the AT&T; version.  Also, the speaker on the back is not centered in the hole.For the price, it is a good case.  It fits the body well.  It is a soft, shiny plastic which looks okay.  It doesn't add much bulk to the phone and looks like it would still give a bit of protection.My biggest issue with the case is that it makes it harder to hit the unlock button on the right side.  Though the plastic feels soft, it isn't very squishy.  I am used to silicone cases which have a lot of give when pushed on.  The hole for the unlock button is not very big.  You have to push the skin of your thumb into the hole to get to the button.  It is not too bad, but a bit annoying.Overall, it is well worth the $3 I paid and makes a good standby until more cases made for the AT&T; version come out.

reviewText: Considering that the price is so low, I was surprised at the quality of the material. It doesn't feel cheap at all. Tho only problem I had was that the hole cut out for the charger was a little smaller than required, so the charger didn't fit initially. I had to scrape out a bit of the material from the hole (not too much of a botheration), and now it can charge without trouble.
